рџ“– Project Overview

The Beauty Products Blog Website is a modern blogging platform that provides information about skincare products, makeup tips, and beauty routines.

This project was created to demonstrate frontend web development skills and digital marketing blog design with a clean layout, animations, and responsive design.

The website includes multiple pages such as Home, Blog, and Contact.

